            "name": "Jérôme Poisson",
            "introduction": "**Jérôme Poisson** is the maintainer of the [Libervia](https://libervia.org/) client, including several components and notably an ActivityPub ⟺ XMPP gateway, and the Libervia Pubsub component (an advanced PEP/Pubsub service). He is also the author of several XEPs and a strong advocate for non-IM use cases, particularly those based on pubsub.",
