        {
            "name": "Arne-Bruen Vogelsang",
            "introduction": "**Arne-Bruen Vogelsang** is the founder and lead developer of [monocles](https://monocles.eu/more/). Whereas he is maintaining two public XMPP servers and [monocles chat]( https://f-droid.org/packages/de.monocles.chat/) is a known XMPP chat client for Android, he's also working on other non-XMPP related open source projects. During his studies he learned a lot about the need for more ethical and fair digital and technological solutions. He also experienced the business side for founding a sustainable company providing open source solutions. He advocates and supports XMPP and open source since many years and is an official XSF member since 2023.",
